Please follow these instructions to locally run the program: 

1. Clone the repository: https://github.com/gecon123/Remesh
2. Through terminal, navigate to the directory where the repo was cloned
3. Install Django with the following command: pip install Django
4. Make sure Django is installed by running: python -m django --version
5. Run the command: source env/bin/activate
6. Navigate into the "mysite" folder
7. Run the command: python manage.py runserver
8. If the browser does not open automatically, navigate to "http://127.0.0.1:8000/app/" on your internet browser
9. To kill the server run the command: CTRL C
10. To kill the environment run the command: deactivate
11. Enjoy!